---
const adoption = [
  { val: "60%", label: "of the top U.S. banks offer Bitcoin services" },
  { val: "90%", label: "of Barron's top 50 RIAs allocate to Bitcoin" },
  { val: "2,000+", label: "advisory firms hold Bitcoin ETFs" },
  { val: "~$28B", label: "U.S. Strategic Bitcoin Reserve, 2025 executive order" },
];

---

<section class="pres-btc">
  <div class="pres-btc__container">
    <div class="pres-btc__intro">
      <p class="pres-btc__eyebrow">The digital reserve</p>
      <h2 class="pres-btc__heading">Why we also <em>stack Bitcoin.</em></h2>
      <p class="pres-btc__body">
        Bitcoin is the only digital asset with a fixed <strong>21 million unit hard cap</strong>
        written into the protocol. It is the scarcest monetary asset humans have ever built, and
        the institutions that spent a decade calling it "internet magic money" are now custodians,
        ETF issuers, and strategic holders.
      </p>
      <p class="pres-btc__body pres-btc__body--italic">
        Our digital reserve is anchored by Bitcoin, with Ethereum held as a secondary allocation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pres-btc__grid">
      <article class="pres-btc__card">
        <h3 class="pres-btc__card-title">What we do with it</h3>
        <p class="pres-btc__card-body">
          We accumulate Bitcoin alongside our real estate operations as a long-term reserve. It is
          <strong>not traded</strong>. Your bond return is <strong>not indexed to Bitcoin
          price</strong>. It is a contractual rate, paid from company cash flows.
        </p>
        <ul class="pres-btc__list">
          <li>Reserve <strong>audited and disclosed</strong> in our semi-annual SEC reporting.</li>
          <li>Held at <strong>BitGo Bank &amp; Trust</strong>, a federally chartered qualified custodian with <strong>$250M of insurance coverage</strong>.</li>
          <li>Balance-sheet hedge against fiat debasement.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="pres-btc__card">
        <h3 class="pres-btc__card-title">Who else is now in</h3>
        <p class="pres-btc__card-body">
          In the last three years the institutional picture flipped. The same firms that declared
          Bitcoin "uninvestable" now custody it, quote it, and in many cases own it.
        </p>
        <ul class="pres-btc__list">
          {adoption.map((a) => <li><strong>{a.val}</strong> {a.label}.</li>)}
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-btc {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-btc__container {
    max-width: 1136px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pres-btc__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pres-btc__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pres-btc__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-btc__heading em {
    color: var(--green-dark);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .pres-btc__body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-btc__heading + .pres-btc__body {
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .pres-btc__body strong {
    color: var(--text-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .pres-btc__body--italic {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .pres-btc__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .pres-btc__card {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(235, 245, 239, 0.5), transparent);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-brand);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pres-btc__card-title {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 130%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-btc__card-body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 165%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-btc__card-body strong {
    color: var(--text-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .pres-btc__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 4px 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .pres-btc__list li {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 160%;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pres-btc__list li::before {
    content: "•";
    color: var(--green-brand);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pres-btc__list strong {
    color: var(--text-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-btc__container {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .pres-btc__intro {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pres-btc__heading {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }

    .pres-btc__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .pres-btc__card {
      padding: 28px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pres-btc__container {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    .pres-btc__heading {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-btc__heading {
      font-size: 3.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1920px) {
    .pres-btc__heading {
      font-size: 3.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
